<TEI.2><text><body><div1 type="alphabetic letter" n="G" org="uniform" sample="complete"><entryFree key="Greatly" type="main" opt="n"><orth extent="full" opt="n">Greatly,</orth> 1) in a high degree, much, very: <bibl n="shak. err 1.2.105" default="NO" valid="yes">Err. I, 2, 105</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. lll 4.2.78" default="NO" valid="yes">LLL IV, 2, 78</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. aww 3.6.58" default="NO" valid="yes">All's III, 6, 58</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. r2 4.263" default="NO" valid="yes">R2 IV, 263</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. r2 5.2.48" default="NO" valid="yes">V, 2, 48</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. 2h6 3.1.281" default="NO" valid="yes">H6B III, 1, 281</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. 3h6 2.6.94" default="NO" valid="yes">H6C II, 6, 94</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. tit 2.3.266" default="NO" valid="yes">Tit. II, 3, 266</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. ham 4.4.55" default="NO" valid="yes">Hml. IV, 4, 55</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. oth 3.1.18" default="NO" valid="yes">Oth. III, 1, 18</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. ant 5.2.14" default="NO" valid="yes">Ant. V, 2, 14</bibl>.<lb />2) illustriously: <emph>small time, but in that small most g. lived this star of England,</emph> H5 Epil. <bibl n="shak. ant 5.2.14" default="NO" valid="yes">Ant. V, 2, 14</bibl> <bibl n="shak. ham 4.4.55" default="NO" valid="yes">Hml. IV, 4, 55</bibl>.
